TOP-SECRET
Model
  - Data Manager: Manages the persistent data of the application

View
  - Interaction Manager: Manages the user/driver interaction and view presentation

Controller
  - Dispatcher: Dispatches messages from MytaxiServiceB to mtaxies driver
  - Queue Manager: Manages the allocation of mtaxies to the city zones
  - Request Manager: Manages business requests
  - Api manager: Manages the API calls from users and authentication procedure
  - ExternalCommunicationManager:
  - Location Manager

Architecture Idea:
  - 3 tier client/server + Pub/Sub

Alg. Ideas
- Given the average number of requests per zone in the last hour and historical data about the numbers of requests per zone
  adapt the distribution of taxies zone per zone
